description: End-to-end employee offboarding orchestration for IT and HR teams. A workflow agent sequences every step — access revocation, device collection, data transfer, and team notifications — while a compliance agent maintains the audit trail. Keep HRIS, Okta, and Jamf as your systems of record; replace the shared Google Doc checklist that always misses a step.
